QuestData.Title: Mawsworn Patrol Map
QuestData.Description:
<A diagram outlining Mawsworn movement patterns has been scrawled onto the parchment.
Ve'nari may find this useful.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Mawsworn Patrol Map to Ve'nari at Ve'nari's Refuge.
QuestData.RewardText:
Valuable information, indeed. This will help me avoid detection whenever I must leave the safety of the refuge.
I trust you've already committed the patrols to memory, Maw Walker.
